%% Diagram: TCP HOL Blocking under HTTP/2
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Server
    participant N as Network
    participant C as Client

    S->>N: Seg 1 (stream 1, CSS)
    S->>N: Seg 2 (stream 3, JS)
    S->>N: Seg 3 (stream 5, img)

    Note over N: Seg 1 dropped

    N->>C: Seg 2 arrives, buffered
    N->>C: Seg 3 arrives, buffered

    Note over C: App sees nothing<br/>(TCP in-order)

    Note over S,C: ~1 RTT later<br/>(retransmit timeout)

    S->>N: Seg 1 (retransmit)
    N->>C: Seg 1 arrives

    C-->>C: TCP releases 1,2,3<br/>to HTTP/2

    Note over C: 3 streams stalled<br/>by 1 lost segment
